Package: DigestionSpecificity
Type: Package
Title: Analyze Cleavage Site Specificity
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kenji OHGANE
Maintainer: Kenji OHGANE <ohgane@me.com>
Description: This package provides a set of functions that allows to plot
    cleavage site specificity based on identified peptide sequences. Both single
    amino acid level plot (barchart) and dipeptide-level specificity (heatmap) can
    be plotted.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    lattice,
    protr,
    viridis
Suggests:
  knitr,
  rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder:
  knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
